                            3 hour - Group Classes - $75 / Person</p>
                        <p>
                            Group Rates Available...</p>
                    </div>
                </section>
                <div class="clearfix">
                </div>
                <section class="seniors">
                    <div class="grid_12">
                        <h2>
                            <strong class="callout">Call Us & Reserve Your Spot Today! (@USFit.Web.Constants.PrimaryPhone)</strong></h2>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </div>
            <div class="clearfix">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
